MAPPING.NAME: m_CLOSEOUT_SHIP_STG

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT a.as_of_date, e.sbu_desc, e.selling_style, comp.parent_item_id, comp.item_id comp_item_id, comp.style_num comp_style_num, comp.color_code comp_color_code, comp.size_code comp_size_code, SUM (a.garments) shipper_garments, SUM (a.dollars) shipper_dollars, SUM (comp_garments) AS comp_garments, SUM (comp_dollars) AS comp_dollars, d.facility_name, comp.lifecycle_code, comp.put_up_cd FROM (select bi.*, i.style_num, i.division_group, i.company_code from bi_inventory bi join slba.item i on bi.item_id = i.item_id where bi.as_of_date = (SELECT AS_OF_DATE - 7 FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE (TRUNC (DAY_DATE) = TRUNC (SYSDATE)))) a JOIN slba_facility d ON a.facility_id = d.facility_id JOIN (select * from slba.style_master_1 where business_seg_desc IN (SELECT DISTINCT SBU_DESC FROM STYLE_MASTER_1 WHERE business_seg_desc IN ('Innerwear', 'Activewear', 'Hosiery'))) e ON a.style_num = e.style_num AND a.division_group = e.division_group AND nvl(trim(a.company_code),'--') = e.company_code JOIN (select u.*, f.style_num, f.color_code, f.size_code from STAGING.STG_CLOSEOUT_INV_UNITS u join slba.item f on u.item_id = f.item_id) comp ON a.item_id = comp.parent_item_id GROUP BY a.as_of_date, e.sbu_desc, e.selling_style, comp.parent_item_id, comp.item_id, comp.style_num, comp.color_code, comp.size_code, d.facility_name, comp.lifecycle_code, comp.put_up_cd

TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_INVENTORY_EXPLODED

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT d.parent_item_id, d.item_id, c.lifecycle_code, SUM (d.garments) comp_garments, SUM (d.dollars) comp_dollars, s.LEGACY_PUTUP_CODE FROM inventory_exploded d JOIN sku_lifecycle_class c ON d.item_id = c.item_id JOIN ITEM I ON D.ITEM_ID=I.ITEM_ID LEFT join sap_item s on i.sap_grid_value = s.grid_value and i.sap_material_num=s.material_num WHERE c.lifecycle_code IN (SELECT Lifecycle_Code FROM lifecycle_class ) AND d.as_of_date BETWEEN c.start_date AND c.end_date AND d.as_of_date = (SELECT AS_OF_DATE - 7 FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE (TRUNC(DAY_DATE) = TRUNC(SYSDATE)) ) GROUP BY d.parent_item_id, d.item_id, c.lifecycle_code,s.LEGACY_PUTUP_CODE

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: EXP to default code, Comp_garments, comp_dollars
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_ASSIGN_VALUES

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT a.as_of_date, e.sbu_desc, e.selling_style, a.item_id AS parent_item_id, a.item_id AS comp_item_id, b.style_num comp_style_num, b.color_code comp_color_code, b.size_code comp_size_code, SUM (a.garments) AS shipper_garments, SUM (a.dollars) AS shipper_dollars, d.facility_name, c.lifecycle_code, s.LEGACY_PUTUP_CODE FROM bi_inventory a JOIN item b ON a.item_id = b.item_id JOIN sku_lifecycle_class c ON a.item_id = c.item_id JOIN slba_facility d ON a.facility_id = d.facility_id JOIN style_master_1 e ON b.style_num = e.style_num AND upper(b.division_group) = upper(e.division_group) AND NVL(trim(b.company_code),'--') = e.company_code LEFT JOIN sap_item s ON b.sap_material_num = s.material_num AND b.sap_grid_value = s.grid_value WHERE a.as_of_date = (SELECT AS_OF_DATE - 7 FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE (TRUNC(DAY_DATE) = TRUNC(SYSDATE)) ) AND c.lifecycle_code IN (SELECT DISTINCT lifecycle_code FROM lifecycle_class ) AND a.as_of_date BETWEEN c.start_date AND c.end_date AND e.sbu_desc IN (SELECT DISTINCT SBU_DESC FROM STYLE_MASTER_1 WHERE business_seg_desc IN ('Innerwear', 'Activewear', 'Hosiery') ) GROUP BY a.as_of_date, e.sbu_desc, e.selling_style, a.item_id, a.item_id, b.style_num, b.color_code, b.size_code, d.facility_name , c.lifecycle_code, s.LEGACY_PUTUP_CODE
